## Title
Dirty Martini Dip

## Recommendation Summary

### Intent Assessment
A savory dip inspired by the dirty martini cocktail. Stub with no ingredients or instructions. Currently categorized under Meals but is really a dip/sauce.

### Categorization Changes
- **PARA**: "resources" → "07-resources" (Correct as reference recipe material.)
- **TREE**: "eat-drink-merriment/meals" → "eat-drink-merriment/sauces/condiments" (RECLASSIFY: This is a dip, not a meal. Should be under sauces/condiments and linked from Recipes - Sauces & Dips instead of Recipes - Meals.)
- **GRAPH**: "links to Recipes - Meals, Food & Nutrition List" → "MOVE parent link from Recipes - Meals to Recipes - Sauces & Dips. Add link to Drinks List (martini connection)" (This is a dip/appetizer, not a main meal. The martini inspiration connects it to the drinks domain.)

