### Enrichment
Dirty martini dip combines cream cheese, sour cream, olive juice/brine, blue cheese, and chopped pimiento-stuffed green olives. Mix with hand mixer, fold in olives and blue cheese, refrigerate 4+ hours (overnight best). Can be made 4 days ahead. Serve with pretzels, crackers, or crostini. Versions exist with and without alcohol. This has gone viral on social media as a party appetizer. Consider serving suggestions and pairing recommendations.

